XML - xtensible markup language 
Used to send data between servers to clients and browsers
Used to configure data and framework in Andriod
Has 2 parts - Layout and Data also known as structure and content of xml 
Needs a root tag
Every opening tag must have a closing tag
whitespace is preserved in xml 
An xml prolog is a term that is used to descripe the version and character encoding in xml 
Xml elements can also have attributes 
Xml files can also work with HTML and CSS code



